    <p>The main page or landing page of the WebHelp Responsive output represents the entry point for
      the WebHelp application. It allows you to easily browse your publication either by choosing
      one of the links to the main topics or by using the search function.</p>
    <p>This page presents links to the main publication topics in two modes: tiles or tree.</p>
