    <section id="main_page_layout_components">
      <title>Main Page Layout Components</title>
      <p>The layout components displayed in the main page are:</p>
      <p>
        <dl>
          <dlentry id="main-page-header">
            <dt>Main Page Header</dt>
            <dd>Main page header area includes the publication title, logo, menu and a link to the
              index terms page.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          
          <dlentry id="publication-title">
            <dt>Publication Title</dt>
            <dd>The title of the publication. It is usually taken from the DITA map title.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          
          <dlentry id="main-page-logo">
            <dt>Logo</dt>
            <dd>Displays a logo associated with the publication. Additionally you can set a target
              URL that will be opened when you click on the logo image.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="publication-menu">
            <dt>Menu</dt>
            <dd>Helps you to navigate to your documentation. This components presents a set of links
              to all topics from your publication.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="index-terms-link">
            <dt>Index terms link</dt>
            <dd>A link to the index terms page.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          
          <dlentry id="search-query-input">
            <dt>Search query input</dt>
            <dd>Input text field allowing you to easily enter your search queries.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          
          <dlentry id="main-page-tiles">
            <dt>Main Page Tiles ares</dt>
            <dd>An area containing tiles for all main topics.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="main-page-tile">
            <dt>Main Page Tile</dt>
            <dd>A tile associated with a main topic. By default it presents the topic title and its
              short description.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          
          <dlentry id="topic-title">
            <dt>Main Page Tile title</dt>
            <dd>Presents the title of the associated topic.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          
          <dlentry id="topic-short-description">
            <dt>Main Page Tile short description</dt>
            <dd>Presents the <xref keyref="dita-spec-shortdesc">short description</xref> of the
              topic. It may be collected either from the topic or from the DITA map topic meta.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          
          <dlentry id="main-page-footer">
            <dt>Main Page Footer</dt>
            <dd>Footer</dd>
          </dlentry>
        </dl>
      </p>
